{"type": "article", "id": 2653, "title": "被“切”成两半的灯具", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-30T07:43:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232350WQKlb8DIpLyvSaM0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自斯洛伐克的设计工作室 MEJD 近日推出两款新颖的灯具，整体造型像是被切成两半一般，其中一盏名为“ Jar ”的吊灯底部呈碗状，上部则像一个水壶，另一盏名为 “ Exhibit ”的台灯像是一个被分成两半的黄铜地球仪。设计师 Štefan Nosko 希望通过这两款花瓶展现斯洛伐克与捷克的工艺水平，尽管整体造型选用了非常典型的形状，但同时赋予了它们新的表现形式。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232347lrIC7gUdW2uQk936.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232348ZbQ3czLXWAdMKkea.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232348bCBeMWJfS2Lk1sUa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232349SUBWX7L06jgCkVQ9.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232349CpMRfkKZBw3rU2QI.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}